<footer>
    <ul class="links">
        {% if page.collection == "posts" %}
        <li class="post-navigation">
            {% if page.previous %}
            <a href="/{{ page.previous.permalink }}"><code>&larr; Previous post</code></a>
            {%- endif %}
            <a href="/"><code>&#8962; Home</code></a>
            {% if page.next %}
            <a href="/{{ page.next.permalink }}"><code>Next post &rarr;</code></a>
            {%- endif %}
        </li>
        {%- endif %}
        <li>‚ù§Ô∏è <a href="https://twitter.com/matthiasendler">Follow me on Twitter</a> and never miss a post again.</li>
        <li>üéÅ <a href="https://tinyletter.com/mre">Subscribe to new articles.</a></li>
        {%- comment %}
        What follows is an ultra clunky way to iterate over a list of social media links.
        This would be much easier with an array slice function.
        {%- endcomment %}
        {%- if page.data.comments %}
        <li>üí¨ Comments available on
            {% for comment in page.data.comments %}
                {%- if forloop.length == forloop.index %}
                {%- if forloop.length > 1 %}
                and
                {%- endif %}
                {{ comment }}.
                {%- else %}
                {%- if forloop.first == forloop.index %}
                {{ comment }}
                {%- else %}
                , {{ comment }}
                {%- endif %}
                {%- endif %}
            {%- endfor %}
        </li>
        {%- endif %}
        {%- if page.data.translations %}
        <li>üìñ Translated into
            {% for translation in page.data.translations %}
                {%- if forloop.length == forloop.index %}
                {%- if forloop.length > 1 %}
                and
                {%- endif %}
                {{ translation }}.
                {%- else %}
                {%- if forloop.first == forloop.index %}
                {{ translation }}
                {%- else %}
                , {{ translation }}
                {%- endif %}
                {%- endif %}
            {%- endfor %}
        </li>
        {%- endif %}
    </ul>
</footer>
